cat << EOF
Kmenc15 is an advanced Qt/KDE MEncoder frontend, generally designed to be a
VirtualDub replacement for Linux. It is most useful for editing and encoding
large high quality AVIs capped from TV. It allows cutting and merging at
exact frames, applying any MPlayer/MEncoder filter, with preview.
